description: Leo's Potato Dumplings is doing lunchtime right on the streets of North Dakota.Taking a passion for cooking and a love of Czech cuisine on the go to you, Leo's is looking out for your taste buds best interests every day.With a menu featuring Kolaches, Czech Fries, and their superb CzechWegian Potato Lefse, you'll certainly find something to love on this food truck.
name: Leo's Potato Dumplings
